  ARRAY['portfolio history is a seismogram of scares','asks for reassurance, trades before it arrives','sleeps in cash, regrets in rallies']::text[] AS t,
  ARRAY['hears "we need to talk" and starts drafting counterarguments','trusts the proven playbook over any clever new idea','treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made','is suspicious of anyone selling a faster method']::text[] AS c,
  ARRAY['keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed','has perfected the art of the reversible half-step','defers the decision until circumstances make it for them']::text[] AS d,
